videos.description: Miles Bridges kicks the pass out to Cassius Winston for the 3-pointer to open up the game.
videos.headline: Winston gets the Spartans started with 3 ball

videos.description: After the block from Jaren Jackson Jr., Cassius Winston lobs a pass up to Miles Bridges at the rim for a two-handed slam.
videos.headline: Bridges throws down alley-oop

videos.description: Notre Dame's Bonzie Colson tries going up with a layup but is blocked by Jaren Jackson Jr.
videos.headline: Michigan State's Jackson Jr. denies Colson

videos.description: Joshua Langford shakes Notre Dame's D.J Harvey with the shot fake and hits the mid-range jumper.
videos.headline: Langford knocks down jumper after pump fake

videos.description: Rex Pflueger finds Martinas Geben cutting down the lane for the emphatic dunk in the first half.
videos.headline: Notre Dame executes inbounds play for open dunk

videos.description: Michigan State's Jaren Jackson Jr. denies TJ Gibbs' shot in the paint for his third block of the half.
videos.headline: Jackson Jr. continues to protect paint with 3rd block

videos.description: Joshua Langford continues his red-hot first half as he knocks down the contested shot.
videos.headline: Langford extends Spartans lead on tough jumper

videos.description: Following a basket from Notre Dame, Miles Bridges limps over to the Spartans' bench for a quick breather before reentering the game late in the half.
videos.headline: Bridges temporarily exits game with ankle injury

videos.description: Notre Dame's Matt Farrell finds Martinas Geben cutting down the lane for the layup early in the second half.
videos.headline: Geben converts layup on pick and roll

videos.description: Notre Dame's Bonzie Colson takes the pass in the post and shakes off Ben Carter for the bucket.
videos.headline: Colson knocks down contested jumper

videos.description: Notre Dame's Matt Farrell breaks out the crossover and steps back to drain the 3-pointer to make it a 10 point game.
videos.headline: Farrell's 3-pointer cuts into Spartans lead

videos.description: Michigan State's Ben Carter hands the ball off to Joshua Langford behind the arch for the 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Carter finds Langford for the 3

videos.description: After initially mishandling the ball, Nick Ward reestablishes his position in the post and knocks down the layup.
videos.headline: Michigan State's Ward nails tough layup

videos.description: Cassius Winston lofts the pass around the rim to Miles Bridges for the emphatic dunk in the second half.
videos.headline: Bridges finishes another alley-oop

videos.description: Seth Greenberg talks with Tom Izzo and Cassius Winston after the Spartans' big 81-63 win over No. 5 Notre Dame. Izzo has critiques for his team's performance and praises the Fighting Irish.
videos.headline: Izzo: 'We got a little complacent'
